:set number will show linenumbers for the file. To remove linenumbers you can use any of the following:<br>
:set number!<br>
:set nu!<br>
:set nonumber<br>
:set nonu<br>
:set nonumber!<br>
:set nonu!<br>

A ! at the end of a set command will toggle the current state of that setting.



